fr.clementgarbay.planner.planning

Class CommonTimeSlotPerson

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.clementgarbay.planner.planning.CommonTimeSlotPerson

  • public class CommonTimeSlotPerson
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a person in a common time slot.

    Note: This object contains a list of availability status which represents the availability of the person for each sub slots (of the duration determined by the time interval of the planner) of the concerned common time slot.

      • getAvailabilityStatusList

        public java.util.List<AvailabilityStatus> getAvailabilityStatusList()
        Get a list of associate availability status for the person in the concerned time slot. For example, if the list is [Available,Available,Unavailable(Préférable)] then this person will be available the first two slots of this common time slot, but will have a "Préférable" priority event the last slot.
        Returns:
        a list
